                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc type="GuestText"><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5805RayaSinB">Vision of Sinodā - Recension B</title>.
                              This text has been added later at the beginning of the volume.</desc>
                           
                           <q xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩፡ አምላክ። ነገር፡ በእንተ፡ ራዕይ፡
